## Main figures for the article

- `Fig_Yahoo_Protocol_Collapse.pdf` — the central figure of the article,
  illustrating the leakage-driven performance collapse.
- `SHAP_summary_v2.png` and `feature_importance_RF_v2.png` — interpretability.
- `yobit_premium_vs_forward_return.png` — empirical illustration of the
  detection-profitability disconnect (Level 4).

## Format note

Figures are saved as PNG (dpi=300) except the main protocol-collapse
figure, saved as PDF for print quality. Convert to PDF/SVG on request if
the target journal requires vector figures throughout.
